metadata.description:

4224 x 2376 px 

A modernist approach to the ancient Arabic folklore stories about Ghouls. The only time they can be seen is during Autumn, when this world and the spirit world are closest.

A collection of 13 artworks. Each piece is made by digitally manipulating a single photograph of an Autumn tree.
